Two big updates: Cline goes scriptable and runs in JetBrains

Hello!

We've been busy lately, and I'm excited to share two updates that make Clin=
e work everywhere you do:

- Cline CLI (Preview)  (https://dxGnp504.na2.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/UF+113/dx=
Gnp504/VVrwbd6HbQgpVsNk1D3yFKzJW861hN75DZdJXN4bXfJ-3lcq-W7lCdLW6lZ3njW83sqj=
