sNksZ7zdJ2LW5YxLp92l4b-Pf6XpK8W04 )  - Native Cline in IntelliJ, PyCharm, W=
ebStorm, and more

Both are powered by Cline Core, the same agent loop we extracted to make Cl=
ine truly platform agnostic.

1. Cline CLI (Preview) - An interactive, terminal-native agent + scriptable=
 infrastructure

Install: npm install -g cline

The CLI isn't just "Cline in your terminal." It's Cline as a building block=
 you can script, automate, and embed anywhere, or simply chat with, just li=
ke in your IDE.

Our wizard Andrei, who led the work on extracting Cline Core, shared a grea=
t deep dive on its architecture and what it unlocks: https://dxGnp504.na2.h=
ubspotlinks.com/Ctc/UF+113/dxGnp504/VVrwbd6HbQgpVsNk1D3yFKzJW861hN75DZdJXN4=
bXfJ-3lcq-W7lCdLW6lZ3njW83sqjw6hYhxdW7_ThQP7rPctxW4qxVl08Q6Y5LW5ffBYp89YVzm=
