GmhW1PY5Zh5HrgsbW2n-B3-2SvWPRf2b72yl04

2. Cline is native in JetBrains

If you're a JetBrains user, Cline now runs natively in your IDE with the sa=
me Plan & Act modes and settings you know from VS Code. Install Cline for J=
etBrains: https://dxGnp504.na2.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/UF+113/dxGnp504/VVrwbd6=
HbQgpVsNk1D3yFKzJW861hN75DZdJXN4bXfJn3lcq-W69sMD-6lZ3nnW7ggklC3ss9rzW61K4wB=
